title: I Have 1 Million Subscribers!?
description:
I'm gonna give Oprah my autograph!! But in all seriousness, thank you to every single one of you for supporting my channel and my videos. I'm so lucky to have such a beautifully positive community and I'm so excited to keep making you laugh (hopefully). If you haven't already subscribed, join the club! 

Writer: Julie Nolke
Actors: Julie & Mirror
Camera: Sam Larson
Editor: Alec Mckay
Production Assistant: Jill Agopsowicz

Also, join my Patreon for behind the scenes videos, live q&as and early access to videos here: https://www.patreon.com/julienolke
